1
00:00:02,296 --> 00:00:05,696
We've come to visit the Tori no Ichi at the Ranburi Shrine.

2
00:00:05,696 --> 00:00:07,496
Ran and Sonoko wanted to come

3
00:00:07,496 --> 00:00:13,196
to choose an oracle that tells fortunes of love, called the Lovely Oracle.

4
00:00:13,196 --> 00:00:15,596
However, the Lovely Oracle

5
00:00:15,596 --> 00:00:17,996
was not the only thing that appeared at Tori no Ichi.

6
00:00:17,996 --> 00:00:19,296
A purse snatcher wearing a funny face mask,

7
00:00:19,296 --> 00:00:21,396
called the Rooster Man also appeared.

8
00:00:21,396 --> 00:00:23,796
Sonoko's bag is also snatched away by this culprit.

9
00:00:24,796 --> 00:00:29,296
We visited the Ranburi Shrine again during San no Tori.

10
00:00:29,296 --> 00:00:31,296
But, there again, Rooster Man appears,

11
00:00:31,296 --> 00:00:34,896
stabs a university student named Mr. Shiro Masuko and wounds him.

12
00:00:36,015 --> 00:00:38,017
Just before passing out,

13
00:00:38,017 --> 00:00:40,019
Mr. Masuko says, "It's not a rooster, but a monkey"

14
00:00:40,019 --> 00:00:42,896
and used fingers of both his hands to indicate the number 9.

15
00:00:42,896 --> 00:00:46,025
What on earth does this mean?

16
00:00:46,025 --> 00:00:49,596
There were three men in the toilet

17
00:00:49,596 --> 00:00:52,031
that Rooster Man locked himself up in.

18
00:00:52,031 --> 00:00:53,296
Mr. Tatsuo Hino,

19
00:00:53,296 --> 00:00:54,896
Mr. Hisami Sarukawa,

20
00:00:54,896 --> 00:00:56,996
or Mr. Shinji Mizunoe?

21
00:00:56,996 --> 00:00:59,796
Is Rooster Man among the three men?

22
00:01:01,296 --> 00:01:03,696
We find out that the button that is found in Ran's coin purse

23
00:01:03,696 --> 00:01:06,045
may be something that Rooster Man had dropped

24
00:01:06,045 --> 00:01:08,396
when he bumped into Ran at the previous Tori no Ichi.

25
00:01:08,396 --> 00:01:12,051
So, the houses of the three men were investigated.

26
00:01:13,596 --> 00:01:15,796
But it looks like this case

27
00:01:15,796 --> 00:01:18,796
is not going to be solved as easily it was first thought to be.

28
00:01:38,077 --> 00:01:39,596
Brooding over passing seasons

29
00:01:39,596 --> 00:01:41,696
will not help in pursuing the mystery of cases.

30
00:01:41,696 --> 00:01:43,296
A mysterious shadow closes in on Ran.

31
00:01:43,296 --> 00:01:46,096
The 9 monkeys and Rooster Man mystery is finally solved.

32
00:01:46,096 --> 00:01:47,496
He sees through the one and only truth.

33
00:01:47,496 --> 00:01:49,296
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

34
00:01:49,296 --> 00:01:51,396
No case is left unsolved with Detective Conan.

35
