63
00:04:29,945 --> 00:04:33,845
By the way, we got a call from the hospital just a while ago

64
00:04:33,845 --> 00:04:37,345
saying that Mr. Shiro Masuko had regained consciousness.

65
00:04:38,257 --> 00:04:41,045
-And? -It seems that he's saying that he has no recollection

66
00:04:41,045 --> 00:04:42,645
