67
00:04:42,645 --> 00:04:44,845
or having said anything about a monkey or the number 9.

68
00:04:44,845 --> 00:04:47,145
I see.

69
00:04:47,145 --> 00:04:50,269
He doesn't remember? What does that mean?

70
00:04:50,445 --> 00:04:53,045
Inspector! I found it!

71
00:04:53,045 --> 00:04:54,845
