00:05:08,287 --> 00:05:11,945
at Ichi no Tori and Ni no Tori confirm whether it was their bags or not.

79
00:05:11,945 --> 00:05:14,293
But since the contents were all out of sorts.

80
00:05:14,545 --> 00:05:15,945
Come to think of it,

81
