00:05:44,323 --> 00:05:47,345
that he stole out and put them back again randomly.

91
00:05:47,345 --> 00:05:50,745
And? Did the victims of Ichi no Tori and Ni no Tori

92
00:05:50,745 --> 00:05:53,945
