93
00:05:53,945 --> 00:05:56,335
Yes, so there's no doubt

94
00:05:56,335 --> 00:05:59,445
that the culprit of all three cases is the same person.

95
00:05:59,445 --> 00:06:01,345
So, now everything is clear, isn't it?

96
00:06:01,345 --> 00:06:02,341
Yeah.

97
00:06:02,341 --> 00:06:06,345
It means that there's a liar among the onlookers here

98
00:06:06,345 --> 00:06:08,945
passing around rumors that Rooster Man ran into the toilet.

99
00:06:08,945 --> 00:06:10,845
True.

100
00:06:10,845 --> 00:06:14,845
Because there seems to be no one

101
00:06:14,845 --> 00:06:19,145
among us who could've visited all three festivals.

102
00:06:19,145 --> 00:06:21,145
Okay then, I guess we get to go.

103
00:06:21,145 --> 00:06:22,361
It's okay, isn't it?

104
00:06:22,361 --> 00:06:24,745
I'm sure my wife is worried to so.

105
00:06:24,745 --> 00:06:27,745
Yes. I guess so, for today.

106
00:06:29,145 --> 00:06:31,445
Move.

107
00:06:31,445 --> 00:06:33,145
Move it, I said!

108
00:06:33,145 --> 00:06:34,645
Strange.

109
00:06:34,645 --> 00:06:36,375
I guess the contents of the bags that were stolen

110
00:06:36,375 --> 00:06:38,377
