that may belong to Rooster Man also bother me.

118
00:06:53,045 --> 00:06:55,345
If Rooster Man was among them,

119
00:06:55,345 --> 00:06:57,245
even if the button didn't come off,

120
00:06:57,245 --> 00:06:58,397
just the thought that it may have,

121
00:06:58,397 --> 00:07:00,845
should've thrown him into panic.

122
00:07:00,845 --> 00:07:03,745
