169
00:09:49,545 --> 00:09:51,845
I'm sorry.

170
00:09:51,845 --> 00:09:55,045
If you really feel bad about it, give us your wallet.

171
00:09:55,045 --> 00:09:56,575
What?

172
00:09:56,575 --> 00:09:58,577
Don't worry!

173
00:09:58,577 --> 00:10:01,045
All we're taking from you is enough to go drinking!

174
00:10:01,045 --> 00:10:03,945
If you mug him, I'm calling the police!

175
00:10:05,845 --> 00:10:08,587
Hey lady, you're punky, aren't you?

176
00:10:08,587 --> 00:10:10,345
