177
00:10:10,345 --> 00:10:12,591
You wanna come play with us?

178
00:10:13,645 --> 00:10:15,730
Those punks.

179
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:19,245
In order to capture that heart of a nervous and old-fashioned type like him,

180
00:10:19,245 --> 00:10:22,245
it's best to be a Japanese woman with all the traditional graces.

181
00:10:22,245 --> 00:10:25,845
Tomboys and girls that prefer flashy fashion are a no-no!

182
00:10:25,845 --> 00:10:29,045
Stay graceful and refined.

