187
00:10:42,345 --> 00:10:45,545
-Hey, let's get out of here -Yeah.

188
00:10:45,545 --> 00:10:46,945
Take care!

189
00:10:52,245 --> 00:10:55,245
Thank you! You're a lifesaver!

