233
00:12:52,545 --> 00:12:54,745
That's why the baseball stadium was named Koshien,

234
00:12:54,745 --> 00:12:56,755
because it was built that year.

235
00:12:56,755 --> 00:12:59,445
Then what is the 9th year?

236
00:12:59,445 --> 00:13:01,645
The 9th is

237
00:13:01,645 --> 00:13:04,245
Koshi, Otchu, Heiin,

238
00:13:04,245 --> 00:13:08,345
Teibo, Boshin, Kishi, Kogo, Shinbi, and

239
00:13:08,345 --> 00:13:09,745
Jinshin.

240
00:13:09,745 --> 00:13:12,045
You mean like in the Jinshin War!

241
00:13:12,045 --> 00:13:15,645
