242
00:13:15,645 --> 00:13:17,845
Like in "Hinoeuma".

243
00:13:17,845 --> 00:13:21,745
The other way of reading for Jinshin is...

244
00:13:21,745 --> 00:13:23,545
Mizunoe, saru...

245
00:13:23,545 --> 00:13:26,345
Mizunoe? Shinji Mizunoe!

246
00:13:26,345 --> 00:13:28,045
It's literally what it is!

247
00:13:28,045 --> 00:13:31,045
As proof of that, the man called Mizunoe,

248
00:13:31,045 --> 00:13:33,145
attempted to show us the receipt he received

